# Care Connect API Documentation — Modules 5 & 6

---

## Module 5: Saved Property API

All endpoints require authentication via `Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>` header.  
Access: Any authenticated role (USER, ASSOCIATE, ADMIN).

---

### 5.1 Save Property

**Endpoint:** `POST /api/v1/properties/{id}/save`

| Parameter | In   | Type | Description                |
| --------- | ---- | ---- | -------------------------- |
| [id](file:///c:/Users/yamit/Downloads/Desktop/livanaFinalbackend/backend-services/src/handlers/listing.rs#301-372)      | path | UUID | ID of the property to save |

**Headers:**

```
Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>
```

**Request Body:** _None_

**Success Response** `200 OK`:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Property saved successfully",
  "data": {
    "property_id": "b3f2c5a1-7e4d-4a89-9c12-3d5e6f7a8b9c",
    "is_saved": true
  }
}
```

> **Note:** If the property is already saved, the endpoint returns the same success response (idempotent).

---

### 5.2 Remove Saved Property

**Endpoint:** `DELETE /api/v1/properties/{id}/save`

| Parameter | In   | Type | Description                           |
| --------- | ---- | ---- | ------------------------------------- |
| [id](file:///c:/Users/yamit/Downloads/Desktop/livanaFinalbackend/backend-services/src/handlers/listing.rs#301-372)      | path | UUID | ID of the property to remove from saved |

**Headers:**

```
Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>
```

**Request Body:** _None_

**Success Response** `200 OK`:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Property removed from saved list",
  "data": {
    "property_id": "b3f2c5a1-7e4d-4a89-9c12-3d5e6f7a8b9c",
    "is_saved": false
  }
}
```

> **Note:** If the property was not previously saved, the endpoint still returns success (graceful handling).

